{"TopicId":216736,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Camera control","CreatedByName":"EvelynThe Dragon","CreatedById":227182,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-19T20:35:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"EvelynThe Dragon","CreatedById":227182,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-19T20:35:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnless I am missing something, it looks like the KSP1 camera control mechanism where you could right-click a part, even on another craft, and focus the camera on it is not part of KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a very bad omission.\u00A0 We really need that functionality in the game, it was essential for me in KSP1, it allowed me to select a docking port as a target on another ship for one thing, making it easier to do a docking maneuver using the Nav-ball markers.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nPLEASE bring this back.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JPR","CreatedById":199326,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-05T17:32:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree -did this get fixed?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"whatsEJstandfor","CreatedById":220814,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-05T20:20:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224300021\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216736\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221688578327\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199326\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JPR\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, JPR said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree -did this get fixed?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/27914-vanamonde/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E said\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/218230-camera-control/?do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=4300027\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehere\u003C/a\u003E, if you middle-mouse click on a part, it will focus the camera on that part, and the center of that part will become the camera\u0027s pivot point\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EvelynThe Dragon","CreatedById":227182,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-07T02:51:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224300054\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216736\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221688588406\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022220814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022whatsEJstandfor\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/5/2023 at 1:20 PM, whatsEJstandfor said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/27914-vanamonde/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E said\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/218230-camera-control/?do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=4300027\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehere\u003C/a\u003E, if you middle-mouse click on a part, it will focus the camera on that part, and the center of that part will become the camera\u0027s pivot point\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is utterly unintuitive, and where is this documented? Do you know?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"whatsEJstandfor","CreatedById":220814,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-07T03:10:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224300406\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216736\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221688698316\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022227182\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022EvelynThe Dragon\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, EvelynThe Dragon said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is utterly unintuitive, and where is this documented? Do you know?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt might be in the control settings but, agreed, it isn\u0027t made obvious; I only know it from word-of-mouth, too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KUAR","CreatedById":229322,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-10T11:20:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224300054\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216736\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221688588406\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022220814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022whatsEJstandfor\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/5/2023 at 9:20 PM, whatsEJstandfor said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/27914-vanamonde/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E said\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/218230-camera-control/?do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=4300027\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehere\u003C/a\u003E, if you middle-mouse click on a part, it will focus the camera on that part, and the center of that part will become the camera\u0027s pivot point\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI thought that was only in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"whatsEJstandfor","CreatedById":220814,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-10T15:23:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224301171\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216736\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221688988005\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022229322\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KUAR\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, KUAR said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI thought that was only in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood call; I didn\u0027t realize we weren\u0027t talking about the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E. In-flight, idk of a way to focus the camera not on the center of mass\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KUAR","Cr